so now we come to my favorite athlete of

00:22:36.400 --> 00:22:39.679
all time

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:42.400
julius eagle

00:22:39.679 --> 00:22:44.320
julius is from kenya and if you know

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:47.200
anything about kenya you know they're

00:22:44.320 --> 00:22:50.000
famous for their long-distance runners

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:52.000
well if you look at julius's arms it's

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:55.120
pretty clear that he's not a

00:22:52.000 --> 00:22:57.280
long-distance runner in fact julius

00:22:55.120 --> 00:22:58.799
always wanted to learn to throw the

00:22:57.280 --> 00:23:01.600
javelin

