but what's the best mixture

00:25:54.240 --> 00:25:58.880
i mean should it be a lot of explicit

00:25:56.880 --> 00:26:00.000
instruction with a with a little

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:03.200
practice

00:26:00.000 --> 00:26:04.720
or a little lecture with lots of active

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:08.400
learning practice

