and then he would go out

00:27:18.080 --> 00:27:20.960
and practice

00:27:20.000 --> 00:27:22.559
watch

00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:25.200
and practice

00:27:22.559 --> 00:27:27.760
watch and practice

