learn by being able to declaratively

00:35:11.920 --> 00:35:15.760
step by step explain whatever they're

00:35:14.720 --> 00:35:18.160
learning

00:35:15.760 --> 00:35:19.839
may impede their ability to learn

00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:22.079
procedurally

00:35:19.839 --> 00:35:24.320
this means it can be difficult for them

