00:38:22.320 --> 00:38:29.200
and allowing them all to flourish

00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:30.480
now how can we best teach students

00:38:29.200 --> 00:38:33.359
well

00:38:30.480 --> 00:38:34.960
retrieval practice is great for teaching

00:38:33.359 --> 00:38:37.920
students to learn through both

00:38:34.960 --> 00:38:40.320
