00:38:37.920 --> 00:38:42.720
spaced repetition also helps students

00:38:40.320 --> 00:38:46.000
learn through both pathways

00:38:42.720 --> 00:38:48.240
straight explanation or lecture helps

00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:50.079
with declarative learning

00:38:48.240 --> 00:38:52.480
but on the other hand varied practice

00:38:50.079 --> 00:38:55.119
and especially interleaving

00:38:52.480 --> 00:38:57.200
help with procedural learning

00:38:55.119 --> 00:38:59.200
what is interleaving

00:38:57.200 --> 00:39:01.920
it means taking

00:38:59.200 --> 00:39:03.040
and mixing closely related ideas

00:39:01.920 --> 00:39:06.320
together

00:39:03.040 --> 00:39:08.480
so that students can begin detecting the

00:39:06.320 --> 00:39:10.560
differences which are sometimes subtle

00:39:08.480 --> 00:39:14.079
as they're practicing

