called blocking

00:39:34.400 --> 00:39:38.560
but if once students first get the hang

00:39:36.960 --> 00:39:41.599
of how to solve a certain type of

00:39:38.560 --> 00:39:44.160
problem they start mixing in problems of

00:39:41.599 --> 00:39:45.119
a different type and then yet another

00:39:44.160 --> 00:39:47.920
type

